Winemakers Brendan and Laura Carter set up the Applewood Distillery in 2012, at their Gumeracha winery in the Adelaide Hills.
The pair are inspired by the history and culture of Australia’s landscape, and have a purist, natural approach. They believe terroir is not just about the elements, it is also about the people - the community of growers and winemakers that surrounds the grapes. Up to 25 native botanicals - including desert lime, wattle seed and peppermint gum leaf - used in Applewood Australian Gin are steeped in high-grade grape spirit, the floral qualities of which balance the astringency of the botanicals.

The grapes are often sourced from growers who cannot sell them elsewhere. Of course, our panel was tasting blind and therefore unswayed by the magic of the story behind the gin. They judged purely on the end result, a gin they praised for its intense eucalypt palate, its uniquely Australian presence and its impressive (locally grown) juniper finish.

description: In the early 1970s, Benriach broke convention in Speyside by returning to distilling batches of whisky in the old, 19th-century style, using malted barley smoked with Highland peat. This wood-rich Highland peat imparts distinctly sweet and smoky notes into Benriach peated whiskies. Benriach Smoky Quarter Cask has been crafted from a combination of unpeated and peated spirit; first matured in bourbon barrels, then undergoing a second maturation in bespoke quarter casks. These smaller quarter casks allow more interaction between the wood and the spirit, intensifying maturation for depth and richness of flavor, to create layers of ripe fruit, fresh wood smoke, and spiced vanilla, with finishing notes of mellow smoke and nutty oak. All in perfect balance.

product_name: YSL MON PARIS FRAGRANCE DISCOVERY MINIATURE SET
description:
MON PARIS, the vertigo experience of l’amour fou. The new feminine fragrance by Yves Saint Laurent invites to lose senses in an upside down Paris. Between passion and freedom, audacity and femininity, the fragrance blends the sensuality of the finest musk with an hypnotic datura accord and the intensity of an exceptional patchouli. Inspired by the modern allure and the edgy couture style of the Yves Saint Laurent woman, the black lavallière unveils the elegance of a multifaceted bottle. MON PARIS, the fragrance of the burning lovers who live and love madly.

LIGHTS ON, HIGH ON LOVE MON PARIS EAU DE TOILETTE LUMIÈRE is a new luminous interpretation of the indelible parisian passion. A fragrance that incarnates the dazzling and vertiginous kind of love that could only take place in the city of lights. Shed a light on the brightest facet of the YSL woman in you, elevated by love. Get high on love. Cry out "Mon Paris, je t'aime!". A CHYPRE FLORAL AQUATIC In this chypre floral aquatic, the intoxicating scent of Datura flower fuses with the luminous aquatic fragrance of the white lotus, a flower that blooms in the water in search of morning light. This luminous and intoxicating facet is contrasted by a Rosa Damascena absolute that is sustainably sourced and crafted for YSL. This bouquet of flowers merges with a bright white patchouli, the chypre signature of the MON PARIS collection. THE BOTTLE In MON PARIS EAU DE TOILETTE LUMIÈRE, the lavallière, the classic pussy bow at the front of the neck of a blouse, takes on a new sophistication. Inspired by Saint Laurent’s transparent pleated blouses, a sheath of black organza in plissé lumière – a technique that reflects the rays of the sun – lets the shiny nude-colored satin ribbon sparkle through, like bare skin covered only by sheer organza. A signature Saint Laurent style statement.

The new MON PARIS INTENSEMENT shouts "Je t'aime" with a precious absolute of Centifolia Rose at heart. It is intense but never dark. It radiates the hot pink glow of passion, turning the white flesh of MON PARIS' hypnotic datura flower into hot fuchsia. The most luminous quality of patchouli flies through the fragrance. Its elegant chypre signature is intensified by gauzy Cashmeran.

To create a more dramatic, lengthened look, repeatedly fluff tips of lashes. Features & Benefits:  Make an impression with this high impact mascara that captures every last lash to lengthen, separate and define for a never ending lash look. Infused with Ceramides for strong, healthier lashes. Clump proof. Smudge Proof. Flake Free.

It takes an inquisitive spirit to produce remarkable results. Through the years PJ Rigney has taken many journeys from the familiar into terra incognita. Those travels brought him here, to the unspoilt landscape of Drumshanbo.  He created The Shed Distillery, with its medieval copper pot stills, and began a quest to fuse oriental botanicals with the local Irish ones.  The result of this exploration is Drumshanbo Gunpowder Irish Gin – unique, extraordinary and as remarkable as the elusive creature PJ has occasionally glimpsed in the fields, the Drumshanbo Jackalope. Alcohol:  43%

Crafted with a nod to a classic London dry style, but with a unique Australian signature. Bright & fresh aromatics from juniper & Australian citrus is balanced with clove, cinnamon, coriander & nutmeg adding rich & warming spice undertones & savoury herbaceous flavours.  Alcohol:  42%

The palate is light bodied and elegant. & Then rose is textural with subtle berry and redcurrant flavours that finishes with a fresh grapefruit citrus core. Alcohol:  0%

Uniquely Australian in style, our whiskey is make from locally sources, single paddock unmalted barley, aged in hand-selected local wine casks, & produced with a focus on quality, bold flavour and sustainable practices. Alcohol:  44%

product_name: YSL Mon Paris Eau de Parfum 50ml
description: REBEL HEARTS DO DECLARE "JE T'AIME" Passionate love is essential and surrender to it's vertigo is an act of audacity. It can turn Paris upside down. And it is all real for those who dare to live it. That is how Parisian lovers feel. The original MON PARIS Eau de Parfum is a striking "Je t'aime!" declaration. The YSL Parisian femininity, both elegant and dangerous, encapsulated in a head-turning scent. The quintessential gift of love to share. THE SCENT OF PARISIAN BLOOMING LOVE MON PARIS is a modern astounding chypre floral. A vertiginous bouquet of daturas: a mysterious flower that only reveals its precious fragrance at nightfall, one that cannot be extracted. That is why YSL uses a patented technology to capture its olfactive snapshot and reproduce it while preserving nature. Dizzying and intoxicating, the datura is completed with aerial and elegant white peony notes; a delicious red-fruity accent; and a sensual, white patchouli essence, a special bright quality for YSL. Precious white musks finish this modern chypre signature. Hypnotic, simply irresistible. A lasting "Je t'aime!" declaration. THE BOTTLE, THE FIRST SEDUCTION One of the most iconic YSL fragrance bottle designs. A multi-faceted glass falcon both feminine and bold, distinctly modern. Quintessentially cool, the lavallière sits securely around the neck of the Mon Paris bottle is made from soft and matte silk, juxtaposed but two rock leather ties and a stylish shining gold YSL Cassandre. At first constrained by the neck-tie, the Mon Paris lover is overcome by a daring power of seduction, the untying of the bow symbolic of the release that comes with love. A fitting tribute to the Mon Paris woman: an elegant allure and an edgy couture style all of its own. Top Notes:  Strawberry, Raspberry, Bergamot essence, Calone Heart Notes:  Pear flesh, Orange flower absolute, Jasmin Sambac absolute, White Peony, Datura Base Notes:  Patchouli essence, White Musk, Ambrox, Cedarwood essence, Cristal Moss Olfactory Family:  White Chypre

Woodford Reserve is created at the historic Woodford Reserve Distillery (Labrot & Graham Proprietors) in Woodford County, the smallest and oldest operating distillery in Kentucky, which dates back to 1812. Woodford Reserve is painstakingly hand-crafted, resulting in a whiskey of exceptional depth and character. This medium-bodied Bourbon's nose is sweet and of citrus, tastes of smokey oak, vanilla and cinnamon and finishes long, round and spicy but mellow. Discover for yourself what discerning critics have deemed one of the very best Bourbons on the market. Woodford Reserve is the Official Bourbon of two of horse racing's most important events; The Kentucky Derby and the Breeders' Cup. Every bottle is individually numbered with the batch number and bottle number. 43.2% Alc./Vol.

product_name: Wolf Blass Platinum Label Cabernet Sauvignon 750ml
description: Complex and opulent, with the fine, layered structure, purity and finesse we have come to expect of the Medlands Vineyard. The palate is focused and precise, with long, textural tannins and an elegant line. Alcohol:  14.5%

Woodford Reserve Double Oaked is matured in separate, charred oak barrels adding a rich and colourful flavour to their Kentucky straight bourbon. Before bottling, the second barrel is deeply toasted before a light charring - extracting additional amounts of soft, sweet oak character. The innovative approach to maturation has crafted a delicious and award winning bourbon whiskey.

The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme, to live everything to excess Libre: Women's Fragrance of Freedom LIBRE Eau De Parfum, the new women’s floral fragrance by Yves Saint Laurent, represents the freedom to live everything to excess. Your boundless creativity, your complete emancipation, your ever-evolving femininity. Libre, the French word for ‘free’, pays tribute to YSL’s most defining value: Freedom. The floral perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experiencing her freedom at its most empowered extreme. A statement women’s fragrance for those who lives by her own rules. Fragrance Scent The first floral lavender. The tension between the burning sensuality of orange blossom from Morocco, the boldness of lavender from France and a daring note of Musk Accord with a feminine twist. A singular trail like a breath of freedom. Fragrance Bottle A couture, sharp-angled bottle that is dually architecturally masculine and sensually feminine. The iconic Libre it-bottle reflects a tension between masculinity and femininity, like a straight geometric silhouette embedded in the smoking jacket. The iconic YSL Cassandre – an oversized luxury accessory – is strikingly bent and nailed into the glass like a jewel. Sexy golden chains and an asymmetric black lacquered cap adorn the bottle to complete it as a manifesto of freedom and irreverence.

A complex, layered nose of lifted blueberry, blackberry and blood plum, with hints of dark chocolate, liquorice and warm spices, enhanced with subtle, fragrant oak. Rich yet elegant, with plush, succulent dark-berry fruit that fills the mouth without being heavy. The tannins are fine, long and velvety, framing the palate while providing texture and length. Alcohol:  14.5%

product_name: Wolf Blass Estates Of The Barossa Dorrien Shiraz 750ml
description: Wolf Blass Estates of the Barossa Dorrien Shiraz is a red wine of purity and structure. Aromas of blueberry and dark chocolate are complemented by a beautifully proportioned palate with definitive line and structural integrity. Tasting Notes: Pure, dark fruit aromas of blueberry, boysenberry and blackberry, with raw dark chocolate, freshly ground coffee beans, and unobtrusive spicy French oak. Alcohol:  14.5%

product_name: Wolf Blass Estates Of The Barossa St John's Shiraz 750ml
description: Wolf blass estates of the barossa st john’s ebenezer road shiraz is a red wine of power and opulence. a sumptuous nose of dark fruits, mocha and charcuterie gives way to a plush, velvety palate restrained with perfectly balanced tannins. shiraz pairs well with grilled, roast and barbecued red meats, dark fruit sauces, mexican, turkish and chinese spices, and smoky flavours. estates of the barossa st john’s shiraz is great with venison, or kangaroo fillet with beetroot relish.

product_name: Yalumba Samuel's Collection Eden Valley Viognier 750ml
description: Pure aromas reminiscent of fresh apricots, lifted ginger and fresh white flowers. The palate is long and silky, with stone fruit flavours, a hint of exotic saffron and finishing with an alluring freshness. 2021 -  Trophy -  Best other white variety or blend - Winewise Championships 2023.   The unmistakeable varietal aroma of apricot is partnered by that of grated ginger root in a vibrant bouquet. Then comes the delightfully textured palate with just-right grip. Viogner, allowed to express itself unchecked can be a loudmouth. This one speaks with decorum, yet leaves no one in doubt of its personality and origin. We urge you to try it Alcohol:  13%

product_name: Wolf Blass Black Label Cabernet Shiraz 750ml 15%
description: The elite parcels of shiraz and cabernet sauvignon selected for wolf blass black label are brought together to form a perfect storm of concentrated power. this wine is the darling of collectors as a result, and it should be yours with its magnificent ability to be a rich and concentrated when young and a wonderfully balanced amalgam of flavours with a touch of bottle age. sublime!

product_name: Wynns The Banker Coonawarra Cabernet Sauvignon 750ml
description: A densely coloured wine with a vivid purple hue. a diverse array of blackberry, dark cherry and black olive, further complexed by notes of liquorice, violets and tobacco. classy oak contributes cigarbox nuances. the rich dark and smooth palate is filled with blackberry and black olive. classic supple, powdery tannins and balanced acidity, frame the dense core of fruit creating a beautifully balanced wine. refined french oak supports the pristine fruit ensuring the wine finishes with poise, balance and seamless length

Intensely deep crimson colour, powerful but full of grace and showing fine balance and structure. The wine opens with spicy blackberry notes. With time in the glass the wine reveals hints of cracked black pepper and then toffee, dark chocolate, and espresso coffee. Richly aromatic and velvety, full bodied and packed with plum, blueberry, hazelnuts, clove, and cinnamon spices. 2021 Winestate Magazine, 98 points - 09 Mar 2023 A classic Barossa shiraz with an inviting combination of sweet dark fruit and chocolaty oak aromas and a palate with a sweet core of varietal fruit and supporting oak. Alcohol:  14.5%

First made in 1982, the john riddoch cabernet sauvignon was conceived as a flagship wine for wynns. john riddoch himself was a true visionary. amongst his many achievements are the building of the wynns gabled winery and the establishment of the coonawarra fruit colony. this wine is made in small quantities from the best available fruit grown on the estate’s extensive cabernet plantings. it has become a definitive coonawarra cabernet sauvignon, made only in years when grapes of extraordinarily high quality are available, using less than one per cent of the top cabernet grapes. concentrated, intricate aromatics of opulent black fruits, fine cedary french oak and complex aromatics, merging with notes of olive and cassis. majestic palate, filled with defined and concentrated flavours of cassis and olive, underpinned by delicate perfumed spice, cedar notes. firm, chalky tannin, vibrant acidity enhance the structure and texture.

Named after david wynn's youngest son, wynns michael shiraz is only being produced when the vintage condition in coonawarra is exceptional. it showcases the unique terroir of the region and with the  release, it displays the qualities that really set it apart with other in the same category. with aromas of red currants, cherries and raspberry that mesh every so well with the olive and white spice characters. the palate follows with an elegant structure bursting with dark brooding spice and succulent ripe tannins. provided with the correct conditions, this could easily be a cellar star.

product_name: Yalumba Samuel's Collection Barossa Bush Vine Grenache 750ml
description: Bright garnet in colour with purple and red hues. Inviting aromas of dark cherries and raspberry amid a floral, spicy background. Time in the glass reveals orange zest, lavender and a tantalising hint of herbes de Provence. This medium–bodied, seductive Grenache shows excellent balance between fruits and spices, silky tannins and lively acidity. 2021 - 92 Points - Halliday Wine Companion, 08 May 2023. Yalumba does grenache very well, from its entry-level wines to its flagship Tri-Centenary offering. The Samuels collection makes use of one of the Barossa's greatest resources: old bush-vine grenache. It's perfumed and lifted with spicy, plummy fruits, a splash of raspberry coulis and plenty of purple floral and gingery spice tones. Purely fruited with plenty of space and inherent drinkability, it's great to see grenache has become 'the next big thing', and for all its pure, joyous fruit, it's easy to see why. Great value here.                                                              2021 - GOLD Medal - Selections Mondiales des vins 2022 Alcohol:  14.5%

Yalumba GEN is a commitment to betterment for the future. Certified organic in 2010, the Carypidis Family Vineyard in Virginia has produced high quality Chardonnay for Yalumba for over twenty five years. They are joined by our organic Chardonnay planting at Waikerie and our first organic grower, the Barich family at Loxton. Meticulous work in all vineyards ensures that the grapes are in perfect condition when they are picked. Alcohol:  12.5%

This Estate Vineyard is located in the heart of Coonawarra. The famous terra rossa soil over limestone is the holy grail of all Cabernet Sauvignon purists. Since 1987, Yalumba has become one of the winemakers fortunate enough to be a part of the inner Sanctum of Coonawarra, crafting wine from exceptional Estate-grown Cabernet Sauvignon. Alcohol:  13.5%

Yalumba GEN is a commitment to betterment for the future. The grapes for this wine are sourced from six family owned, certified organic vineyards. The Barich family on the Murray River at Loxton, the Strachan family in McLaren Vale, the Palena family in the Riverland and the Carypidis family in Virginia have been the long term growers and the backbone of this wine. Since 2018, we have also sourced grapes from the Strachan family at Renmark and our own vineyard at Waikerie. Alcohol:  14%

Yalumba GEN is a commitment to betterment for the future. Certified organic in 2010, the Carypidis Family Vineyard at Angle Vale has produced high quality Pinot Grigio for Yalumba for more than ten years. Meticulous work in the vineyard ensures that the grapes are in perfect condition when they are picked. Alcohol:  12.5%

Yalumba GEN is a commitment to betterment for the future. Beautiful organic Viognier grapes are picked from the Barich family property adjacent to the Murray River at Loxton, the Bassham family’s vineyard in Barmera and the Yarra Vale Vineyard in Virginia. Meticulous work in all vineyards ensures that the grapes are in perfect condition when they are picked. Alcohol:  13%

The Virgilius is our flagship white wine. After more than 40 years of working with this variety, the cool elevated slopes of Eden Valley has proved its place in the world as one of the great homes of Viognier. Handpicked and wild fermented in old French oak, this is wine with layers of richness, complexity, fine textures and flavours. Alcohol:  13.5%

A flagship Shiraz born of treasured, old vines dating back to 1854, these are some of the oldest Shiraz plantings in the world. Matured in Yalumba coopered oak octaves; the inspiration behind the name of this fine, Barossa wine. Alcohol:  14%
Each vintage of The Signature is named in honour of an individual who has made a significant contribution to the culture and traditions of Yalumba. Alcohol:  14.5%

Handpicked from old, gnarly bush vines planted in 1889 in two acres of deep sandy loam soil over red-brown clay in the heart of the Barossa Valley. Year after year these ancestor vines give small quantities of exceptional grapes. Alcohol:  13.5%

The Caley is the pinnacle of a long winemaking journey of excellence, that rightfully honours one of Yalumba’s most adventurous sons. A blend of Coonawarra Cabernet Sauvignon and Barossa Shiraz, The Caley is a classic marriage of two noble varieties and two great Australian wine regions. Alcohol:  14%

The world's leading brand of premium tequila, a dark amber with copper highlights that spends 3 years in French oak. Rich in flavour, smooth, rounded with spicy agave taste. It has aromas of oak driven agave with caramel, vanilla and toasted coconut, and a pleasantly spicy finish.

Smooth and medium bodied tequila with notes of Coconut.   Named in commemoration of the year in which the first expertly crafted tequila was unveiled, 1800 tequila still follows the standards of the original formula, created in the year 1975. 1800 Coconut is created by infusing Jose Cuervo's signature 100% Agave double-distilled 1800 Silver Tequila with natural, ripe Coconut flavour. With its slightly-sweet and medium bodied tropical taste, this versatile spirit is delicious on the rocks and tastes great mixed with pineapple juice.     Crystal clear colour with blonde highlights   Tasting notes - nose: soft and tropical with sweet Agave   Tasting notes - palate: smooth and medium bodied with notes of Coconut   Tasting notes - finish: long, subtle sweet Coconut in the finish   ABV 35%

product_name: Yalumba The Menzies Coonawarra Cabernet Sauvignon 750ml
description: In 1992 the Hill-Smith family counted themselves amongst those fortunate enough to own a vineyard upon the famous Coonawarra terra rossa soil over limestone. Experimentation, innovation, minimalist intervention and small batch winemaking has resulted in The Menzies’ reputation as a wine of longevity, elegance and structure. Alcohol:  14%

Dow's old Tawnies are well known for their remarkable raisiny, dried fruit flavours, exquisite creamy texture and an exceptionally long, lingering and traditionally drier finish. This 10 Year Old Port is smooth, well balanced and mature and is ready for drinking now. Dow's 10 Years Old Tawny has a bright tawny colour. On the nose brimming with aromas of candied fruit and toffee, beautifully combined with some mature ripe fruit. On the palate vibrant nutty flavours, perfect balance and with a lovely long finish. Alcohol:  20%

An ultra-premium clear Añejo Tequila finished in port wine casks. 1800® Cristalino is a beautiful contradiction. It is aged in French and American oak barrels, married together, then rested in port wine casks. Finally, it is meticulously filtered to crystal clear clarity while retaining the depth and complexity of Añejo along with the silky smoothness of a Claro. Alcohol:  35%

product_name: YSL Black Opium Eau de Parfum 50ml
description:
An Edible Floral Oriental Fragrance Top Notes - Par accord, Mandarin essence Middle Notes - Orange blossum asbolute, Jasmine absolute Base Notes - Black coffee accord, Vanilla absolute, Patchouli  
 The Inspiration: 
 Black Opium Eau de Parfum is a modern glam rock version of a classic feminine scent. Designed like a shot of adrenalin, this fragrance will stop them intensely in their tracks. 
 The Personality: 
 Assertive and unique, the Black Opium woman embodies the new Yves Saint Laurent spirit. Free and self-confident, she expresses a femininity glamourous yet impertinent. Always searching for new experiences, nothing will stop her.

Jose Cuervo's signature double-distilled 1800® Silver Tequila infused with natural, ripe coconut flavor. With its slightly-sweet and medium-bodied tropical taste, this versatile spirit is delicious on the rocks and also tastes great mixed with pineapple juice. Alcohol:  35%

Celebrated in exclusive cocktail bars, restaurants and nightclubs, the iconic Don Julio 1942® Tequila is the choice of connoisseurs around the globe. Produced in small batches and aged for a minimum of two and a half years, Don Julio 1942® Tequila is handcrafted in tribute to the year that Don Julio González began his tequila-making journey. Tasting Notes: Nose: Rich caramel and chocolate Taste: Warm oak, vanilla and roasted agave Finish: Lingering oak and rich vanilla Alcohol:  38%

product_name: YSL Libre Absolu Platine Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: LIBRE L'ABSOLU PLATINE, the new feminine perfume by Yves Saint Laurent, the absolute intensity to burn from cold & shiver from heat. The perfume of a strong, bold and free woman experimenting her freedom absolutely. A new clash of desirability, inspired by the two most precious materials of the world blending together: gold & platinum. The hottest jewel-like bottle, encapsulating a unique metallic trail with the highest concentration within the LIBRE range. A new absolute & unmistakable intensity, evoking a fiery burn and a shiver-inducing chill all at once. A new tension between hot and cold, like a cutting-ice breath of freedom. Indulge in the luxurious scent of LIBRE L'ABSOLU PLATINE and experience the absolute freedom.

The grapes used in the production of Dow's Fine Ruby were a blend of traditional Portuguese varieties from the Douro Valley, such as Touriga Nacional, Touriga Franca, Tinta Barroca, Tinta Roriz and Tinto Co. Dow's Fine Ruby was aged in seasoned oak casks at our lodges in Vila Nova de Gaia for an average of 3 years and bottled when ready to drink. Exuberant youthful fruit flavours make it perfect for informal drinking. Alcohol:  19%

Don Julio is one of the most famous tequilas in the world. Unlike other añejo tequilas that are aged for the legal minimum of one year, Don Julio Añejo is matured in reclaimed American oak whiskey casks for 18 months. This creates a complex and discernible range of flavors from exquisite citrus fragrances to the complex sweetness of rich honey and vanilla. Don Julio Añejo tequila is made from 100% blue agave. This is exclusively cultivated to the exact specifications outlined by Don Julio. Tasting notes: It has rich notes of red fruit and butterscotch, with a lightly spiced finish Alcohol:  38%

LIBRE, the new Eau de Toilette by Yves Saint Laurent. The fragrance of a sensual & irreverent woman unveiling a new undressed freedom, the freedom to live everything on the skin. LIBRE, THE NEW EAU DE TOILETTE BY YVES SAINT LAURENT Created by the master perfumers Anne Flipo & Carlos Benaim to unveil a new sensual & undressed freedom, The freedom to live everything on the skin. With initiatives of exceptional sourcing around the world, YSL BEAUTY selects precious natural ingredients that define the uniqueness of the scent of freedom. WHAT IT IS The iconic structure of LIBRE, a tension between noble orange blossom from Morocco and sustainably sourced lavender from France, exclusively crafted for Yves Saint Laurent, is reinterpreted in a modern, bright and fresh sensuality. The carnal femininity of orange blossom absolute is infused with a pure white tea accord, exacerbating the warm-cold duality of the fragrance to leave a shivering yet sun-kissed sensuous pleasure. The iconic LIBRE IT-bottle is reinvented in a new elongated shape whose vertical extension clashes with the couture extravagance of the gold oversize horizontal Cassandre bent & nailed into the glass. Libre Eau de Toilette encapsulates a new delicate golden pink fragrance shade, celebrating femininity on the edge of nude. The embodiment of a new undressed freedom.

Don Julio Blanco is the base from which all of our other variants are derived. Commonly referred to as "silver" tequila, its crisp agave flavor and hints of citrus make it an essential component to a variety of innovative drinks including margaritas. It can also be enjoyed neat or on the rocks.   Tasting notes: Crisp agave aroma blended with fresh citrus and sweet flavours providing a dry finish. Alcohol:  38%

Dow's Fine Tawny is a three-year-old blend aged in small oak casks at our lodges in Vila Nova de Gaia. The barrel ageing produces a smoother and lighter style of wine than the Dow's Ruby which is aged primarily in large oak vats and tonels. Dow's Tawny combines subtle fruit with delicious velvety nutty flavours derived from the cask ageing. It is ready to drink and enjoy when bottled and does not require further ageing. Alcohol:  19%

product_name: YSL Y Reno Eau De Toilette 100ml
description: Creative. Doer. Accomplished.  How to use:  Perfume on the 3 pulse points: wrist, inner elbow and neck. Notes: - Bergamot Essence Aldeyhdes Ginger Essence - Lavander Heart Geranium Heart Clary sage Heart - Cedarwood Essence Olibanium Essence Ambergris accord

product_name: YSL Mon Paris Fragrance Discovery Miniature Set
description: Discover this exclusive 4-piece miniature set, featuring Mon Paris Eau de Parfum, a sweet floral perfume for women; Mon Paris Eau de Toilette Lumière, a light and dazzling fruity floral perfume capturing the essence of spring in the city of love; and Mon Paris Intensément, the new daring take on the classic Eau de Parfum. This set contains:  2 x 7.5ml YSL Mon Paris Eau De Parfum, 1 x 7.5ml Mon Paris Eau De Toilette Lumière, 1 x 7.5ml Mon Paris Intensément How to use:  Apply fragrance on the warmer areas of the body: behind your neck, onto the inside of your wrist and underneath your earlobes. Alternatively, spray generously in front of you and walk forward to immerse yourself in the scent. Apply Rouge Pur Couture starting at the center of the lip and gliding to the corners. Then reverse the movement for maximum color impact. Start applying at the root of the lash on the outside of the eye. Apply the brush to the lash, pushing upwards and outwards at the same time with a zig-zag type of movement. On the inner & bottom lashes, use just the tip of the brush and apply to individual lashes.

What it is

Zacapa Solera Gran Reserva is a a complex and full-bodied dark rum. Aged in ex-American Whiskey and ex-Sherry casks to deliver flavour notes of raisined fruit, Zacapa Solera Gran Reserva can be enjoyed neat, on the rocks or to give classic cocktails  like an Old-Fashioned a delicious twist.  Tasting notes:It has a sweet honeyed viscosity more reminiscent of a liqueur than an aged spirit; a great depth of raisined fruit and apricot preserves, building to an intense heart of savoury oak, nutmeg, with notes of coffee and delicately sweet vanilla, balanced with a spicy touch of cinnamon and ginger on the pleasantly astringent finish; truly a rum for the discerning
palate.

Our classic vodka is infused with a hint of Aussie playfulness, it's a lively dance on the palate. Smooth, crisp and utterly enjoyable - an embodiment of sun-soaked joy & something truly Australian. To be swirled, sipped, savoured and shared. Alcohol:  37%

Balanced with juniper, pepper berry, coriander, cinnamon myrtle, camomile, and strawberry gum the botanicals are distributed across six botanical baskets and slow steeped in our sugarcane spirit for up to two days. Aroma: Orange peel, juniper, floral & spice Palate: Citrus, herbal, eucalypt & floral Mix With: Dry Tonic Garnish With: Orange & thyme Alcohol :40%

Organic Mulberries are harvested for this seasonal treat. The spirit is infused with juniper for 48 hours, then orange zest takes a brief dip before whole mulberries are introduced and steeped for 5 days.   Aroma: Fruity & fresh Palate: Berry, herbal & peppery  Mix With: Soda water Garnish With: Lime & Star Anise  Alcohol: 40%

Alcohol:  40%

Pure, smooth Australian sugarcane spirit is distilled with traditional juniper and Australian native botanicals lemon myrtle, cinnamon myrtle, pepper berry, finger lime and wattle seed. Butterfly pea are steeped in the liquid for 18 hours to bestow their natural blue tint. This is sensitive to pH and transforms to delicate violet with added acidity such as tonic or lemon. Aroma: Herbal, Lemon Myrtle Palate: Lemon Myrtle, Cinnamon Myrtle, Cardamom & Pepper Berry Mix With: Dry Tonic Garnish With: Orange & Rosemary Alcohol: 40%

Tasting Notes: Luxurious passionfruit and mango aromas mingle with the herbaceous lift of red juniper. On the palate, sweet and juicy pineapple and mango layer with zesty citrus notes from the finger lime and lingering juniper pine-spice warmth. Sip neat or mix with soda, tonic or fresh pineapple juice, plenty of ice and a mint garnish. Alcohol:  40%

Intense aromatics of melon, white peach, and grapefruit combined with tones of toasty oak. The palate is fresh and lively, with rich flavours of peach, white stone fruit and grapefruit which is balanced with creamy, opulent texture and a delicate sweetness that comes from the complex oak characters. The length is generous and perfectly balanced. Alcohol:  0%

400 Conejos Espadin Joven is produced by maestro mezcalero Don Tacho in Santiago Matatlan, Oaxaca. Don Tacho carefully selects the agave Espadin when they have reached maturity after 8-10 years. This mezcal is traditionally produced using a stone oven (horno), horse-drawn tahona, and copper distillation. Mezcal 400 Conejos is named after the ancestral belief that agave spirits were occupied by 400 rabbits. Those who ingested the agave spirits would be controlled by one of the 400 rabbits, but no one ever knew which rabbit you’d get with each mezcal. Each rabbit had a different personality and way of making you think and act. Mezcal 400 Conejos’ expressions are made with agave Espadin, and their mezcal is marketed mostly for cocktails.

A superb example of coonawarra’s cool climate style, this wine displays great fruit character, rich and complex flavours of red berries, spice and chocolate with layered fruit underpinned by tightly-focused tannins. dark and focused, filled with juicy and vibrant fruit. blood plum and magnolia pervade the mid palate. sleek, plush tannins frame the bright fruit creating a seamless, layered wine, telling of its cool climate home. 'excellent depth to the colour heralds a wine replete with an abundance of purple and black fruits seamlessly woven together on the medium to full-bodied palate, oak and tannins provide the framework for a wine with a very long life ahead.'

product_name: Versace Eros Flame Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: A fragrance that hits straight to the heart, which conveys an important message to the new generations about the dignity of love and the power of diversity. Versace Eros Flame is the fragrance for a strong, passionate and self-confident man who lives his emotions on the skin.The olfactory notes of Versace Eros Flame are characterized by strong contrasts in which the noblest and most elegant ingredients are enriched and enhanced with each other. the others: lemon, mandarin, orange, black pepper, wild rosemary, pepperwood, geranium, rose facets, cedar, patchouli, tonka beans and vanilla. A persistent and enveloping fragrance, which manages to be virile at the same time, an ode to passion and a hymn to the voluptuousness of the senses. Ingredients: SD Alcohol 39C, Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Limonene, Linalool, Coumarin, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Alpha-Isomethy Ionone, Citronellol, Citral, Ethyhexyl Salicylate, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Geraniol, Isoeugenol How to use:  Apply your perfume to pressure points for a long lasting scent at the inner wrists, the base of the throat, behind ear lobes and in the cleavage. As you wear your perfume throughout the day, it will react with your body heat and continue to emit scent. Fragrance Notes:  Hesperidic, Amber, Woody, Chinotto Accord, Black Pepper, Rosemary, Patchouli Coeur, Haitian Vetiver

Vantage Australia set out to capture the essence of this sunburnt  country and bottle the flavours of the bush to create its own unique  native spirit. Inspired by Australia’s own native flora, Vantage  was developed using only premium botanicals. Lemon myrtle  and Tasmanian mountain pepper were distilled creating a smoky  bush flavour complemented with a hint of zesty mandarin oil from  Australian grown mandarins. Vantage Australian Botanical Spirit at 37% ABV cuts  across the traditional spirit categories of gin, vodka and white rum

product_name: Valentino Donna Born In Roma Green Stravaganza Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: As the sun rises and shines over the eternal city, Born in Roma Green Stravaganza takes you on a bold adventure to the cool gardens of Roma where you are free to live and express your unique ways.  Born from the abundant gardens of Roma, this floral-ambery woody fragrance opens the door to an extravagant world created by distinctive lapsang souchong tea accord and radiant jasmine absolute with a captivating touch from vanilla extract. Born in Roma Green Stravaganza leads a way into the extravagance of Roma, allowing cool kids to feel the energy, unleash their personalities, and live excessively, because there are many vibrant ways to be you. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: Opening with a smoky tea leaves scent, this fragrance draws you into a sensual garden with Lapsang Souchong tea accord. Heart Note: Delicate jasmine absolute illuminates the heart of the mix with its solar and floral facets, unveiling modern feminity of this note. Base Note: Sweet yet smoky drops of vanilla extract add a bewitching touch to this sensual journey, pushing the extravagance to extremes.

description: With Born in Roma Yellow Dream, Valentino opens a new chapter for a world that needs to dream. The color of Rome, bathed in yellow light, to inspires dreams of tomorrow, new beginnings for now. Signed by the depth and warmth of Rome’s light, Born in Roma Uomo Yellow Dream is a spicy oriental fragrance, built around a tension of comfort and floral notes. It is given an unexpected, generous addiction with a sensual vanilla accord. Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: Spicy with a hint of freshness, the cinnamon in this scent compliments the sweet and comforting aroma it holds. Heart Note: Lavandin creates a blooming sense of freshness. The aromatic and floral notes give a refreshing texture to the scent, bringing a level of timeless yet familiar refinement. Base Note: Evolving into a warm and woody scent, the vanilla adds a wholesome and rich touch to finalize the bouquet created by this fragrance.

product_name: Valentino Donna Born In Roma Yellow Dream Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: With Born in Roma Yellow Dream, Valentino opens a new chapter for a world that needs to dream. The color of Rome, the eternal city bathed in yellow light, inspires dreams of tomorrow, new beginnings for now. Born from the dream of Rome, bathing in a golden light, this floral perfume, created from the scent of a thousand rose petals is reinforced by the contrasting scent of musks. A scent full of optimism and energy. Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: The delicacy of a peony accord captured in a scent. Like the flower, the fragrance’s petals peel one by one, offering a fresh and airy aroma at the top of this note. Heart Note: An airy bouquet blooms at the heart of this fragrance. Led by a delicate Turkish rose essence, obtained by re injecting rose water into a solid form revealing the flower’s fresh green facets, together with its silky, opulent trail. Base Note: This floral heart is soothed by the reassuring, comforting notes of a pure accord. Then in total contrast, the dry down is teased by the power of white musk a sensual white musk overdose that develops into a lingering powdery softness.

product_name: Valentino Voce Viva Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: The sound of your voice, the scent of your fragrance, both a magnetic presence. Voce Viva celebrates every woman’s unique voice in one declaration: My voice, My strength. An invitation to voice dreams, and to live them. Voce Viva, a living voice. A floral reimagining in the spirit of Valentino’s contemporary femininity - couture Orange Blossom absolute and golden Gardenia accord paired with colorful Italian Bergamot and Mandarin. This harmony is made unexpectedly addictive through a surprising layer, a traditionally masculine accord of Crystal Moss with an infusion of Vanilla. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: A colorful and sparkling opening of Italian Bergamot is softened by sweet and juicy mandarin. Heart Note: An opulent bouquet of Orange Blossom absolute is refreshed with a Golden Gardenia accord. Base Note: An unexpected Crystal Moss brings a modern intensity to the base, becoming wholly addictive by the addition of an enveloping vanilla infusion.

product_name: Valentino Donna Born In Roma Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Inspired by Rome, a place where past and present coexist, Born in Roma fragrances tell a story of self-expression: a celebration of people living life freely, while embracing their heritage. Born in Roma is a modern Haute Couture floriental. A couture elegance made of Sambac Jasmine to bring a luxurious femininity when blended with Vanilla Bourbon, the most expensive extract in the world. This mix is twisted with a radiant trio of modern woody notes, with a cashmeran accords, for an edgy touch inspired by Rome’s street culture today. Born in Roma fragrance collection: Many ways to be you. Celebrate your uniqueness with 3 duos to reveal the different aspects of your personality. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: Considered one of the most luxurious ingredients in perfumery, jasmine has been an icon of femininity for centuries. Heart Note: An unusually spicy note adds a layer to the multi-facetted note, bringing a lively turn to this sensual note. Base Note: A refined sense of darkness doubled with extreme sensuality, crucial to the intensity of the signature. Its drydown is spicy and carnal, sensual and distinctive bringing an irreverent twist to the fragrance.

description: Inspired by Rome, a place where past and present coexist, Born in Roma fragrances tell a story of self-expression. The composition opens with bergamot and myrtle, succeeded in the heart by roasted coffee combined with gianduja cream, on a rich base created of cedar and precious leather. D&C VIOLET NO. 2 (CI 60730), FD&C BLUE NO. 1 (CI 42090), FD&C RED NO. 4 (CI 14700).

Designed for living life in elegant irreverence, Valentino Donna is full of life, and romantic. Inspired by Rome, where past and present coexist, it tells a story of independent passion. A timeless floral scent, created around the distinct couture elegance of opulent Iris notes, Donna Eau De Parfum juxtaposes the flower’s powdery femininity with the mysterious sensuality of Turkish Rose accords, modernized with a touch of Patchouli. Fragrance Notes: Top Note: The opulence of Turkish rose is one like no other. It brings a light to the bouquet, redefining femininity and reframing the softness of a silky scent. Heart Note: Iris’s sophistication complexifies the fragrance, with an elegant twist and a powdery element. Base Note: At the base, patchouli’s woody and earthy notes deepen the bouquet into a powerful chypre scent, tying the fragrance together.

product_name: Valentino Uomo Acqua Eau De Toilette 125ml
description: Valentino uomo acqua is a contemporary exploration of lightness and intensity. the top notes reveal the aromatic freshness of an italian garden with green tomato, clary sage and a hint of mandarin and citron, which are offset by the dark and velvety depth of iris absolute, white leather and patchouli heart. valentino uomo acqua is presented in the iconic studded glass bottle reinterpreted to convey the idea of freshness. the finely crafted bottle is an evolution of the aesthetics of the classic valentino uomo fragrance and creates a new expression of beauty in perfumery.

product_name: 3sixT Hi-Res Audio 3.5mm Cable 0.1m USB-C Connector For Headphones Black
description: The 3sixT Hi-Res Audio Connector is a short-length cable engineered to provide high-fidelity sound transmission between USB-C enabled devices and 3.5mm audio interfaces. Its sleek design and durable construction make it an ideal accessory for audiophiles and music enthusiasts seeking uncompromised audio quality on the go.

Love, passion, beauty and desire: these are the key concepts of the new Versace men's fragrance. Male body as an aggregate of perfect forms. The allusion to classical Greek mythology is back in the Versace world: Eros, the god of love, capable of making people fall in love with an arrow of love. Versace Eros is the fragrance for the strong, passionate and self-possessed man. Ingredients: Alcohol, Denat. (Sd Alcohol 39 C), Fragrance, Water, Limonene, Ethylhexylmethoxycinnamate/ Butylmethoxydibenzoylimethane/Ethylhexylsalicylate, Coumarin, Linalool, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Citronellol, Citral, Geraniol, Cinnamal, Eugenol How to use:  Apply your perfume to pressure points for a long lasting scent at the inner wrists, the base of the throat, behind ear lobes and in the cleavage. As you wear your perfume throughout the day, it will react with your body heat and continue to emit scent. Fragrance Notes: Fresh, Oriental, Woody, Lemon Italy Opur, Ambroxan, Geranium Flower, Vetyver

description: Yellow Diamond is crafted as a pure, transparent and airy floral fragrance, sparkling and intense as the yellow color, while being luxurious and feminine like a diamond. Its composition opens with luminous freshness of lemon, bergamot, neroli and pear sorbet. The heart features airy orange blossom, freesia, mimosa and water lily. The base is made of amber, precious musk and guaiac wood. Experience Versace Yellow Diamond with this 3 oz Eau de Toilette Spray. Ingredients: Alcohol Denat. product_name: Versace Bright Crystal Eau De Toilette 90ml
description: A sensual and feminine fragrance, symbolising the Versace woman who is confident and sure of her charm. It is a fragrance that reveals juicy yet delicate notes that delight the senses. Fragrance Notes: Top: Yuzu, iced accord, pomegranate Heart: Peony, magnolia, lotus flower Base: Acajou, vegetal amber, musk Olfactory family: Floral, fruity, musky

description: A strong, masculine fragrance, Dylan Blue encapsulates the sensual scents of the Mediterranean. The fragrance with strong aquatic notes is refreshed with citrus hints of bergamot and grapefruit, enriched with spicy notes of rare saffron and musky base notes. Fragrance Notes: Top: water notes, fig leaves, bergamot, grapefruit Heart: Violet leaves, patchouli, papyrus, black pepper, ambroxan Base: Musk, tonka beans, saffron, frankincense Olfactory family: aromatic

An alchemy of seductive, luminous and feminine notes with Sicilian lemon, Calabrian bergamot and pomegranate seeds to amaze and seduce. A refined accord of lemon and jasmine that conveys an authentic and timeless femininity. The mysterious and intense ambrox reveals the passion together with sensual and soft woods, the dense sandalwood and the intoxicating musk. Ingredients: Alcohol Denat. (Sd Alcohol 39-C), Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Limonene, Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Citronellol, Hydroxycitronellal, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Linalool, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Geraniol, Citral, Farnesol, Cinnamyl Alcohol, Benzyl Benzoate, Benzyl Alcohol, Ci 19140 (Yellow 5), Ci 17200 (Red 33). For the man whose strength is his soul, who feels free and knows how to enjoy life bit by bit, Versace Man Eau Fraiche, a new harmony of scent where the most classic ingredients of mens' scents are refreshed with unusual notes, giving life to a surprisingly fresh fragrance. In 1818, Madame Clicquot invented the first known blended Rose Champagne ever that you can enjoy and share today for its liveliness and burst of fruits. A fruity and full-bodied expression of the Veuve Clicquot style. 750ml 12%

product_name: YSL Libre Flowers & Flames Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Libre Flowers & Flames Is A New Sultry Floral Blast. A Sexy Warm Reinterpratation Of Libre, Deliberatly Sensual & Floral. The Hot & Powerful Lily From The Desert Blends With The Solar & Creamy Coco Palm Tree Flower, For A Blazing Yet Comforting Scent. Fragrance Notes: Top Notes: Lavender Heart & Bergamotte Essence Heart Notes: Lily Flower accord, Palm Tree flower accord, Orange blossom, Diva Lavender Base Notes: Vanilla

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Spicebomb Eau De Toilette 90ml
description: The bottle of the fragrance Spicebomb is a real luxury object: after being fashioned like a diamond for Flowerbomb, the grenade is reinvented in a glass sculpture with chased, even and masculine facets. The ultimate detail: the fragrance is released by priming the pin, which has been revisited with the Viktor&Rolf seal. The olfactory explosion is inescapable.

product_name: Veuve Clicquot Traveller’s Exclusive Yellow Label Brut 750ml
description: Since its foundation in 1772, Veuve Clicquot champagne has travelled across the oceans, faithful to Madame Clicquot's goal of "crossing borders" and bringing the finesse of her champagne all around the world. This travel edition collection is a subtle wink to her visionary spirit. Discover the insert that turns into a postcard. Tasting Notes: Veuve Clicquot Sydney TREX manages to reconcile two opposing factors - strength and silkiness - and to hold them in perfect balance with aromatic intensity and a lot of freshness. The predominance of Pinot Noir provides the structure that is so typically Veuve Clicquot, while a touch of Meunier rounds out the blend. Chardonnay adds the elegance and finesse essential in a perfectly balanced wine. This consistent power to please makes Veuve Clicquot Sydney TREX ideal as an apéritif, and perfect as the champagne to enjoy with a meal. Blend : 50-55% Pinot Noir / 28-33% Chardonnay / 15-20% Meunier (40 to 45% Reserve Wines) ABV : 12%

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Spicebomb Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: The bottle of the fragrance spicebomb is a real luxury object: after being fashioned like a diamond for flowerbomb, the grenade is reinvented in a glass sculpture with chased, even and masculine facets. the ultimate detail: the fragrance is released by priming the pin, which has been revisited with the viktor&rolf seal. the olfactory explosion is inescapable.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Flowerbomb Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: This fragrance is a more sensual, more Oriental version of the Eau De Parfum Flowerbomb. More concentrated, hence more glamorous and chic. Scent starts with bergamot, sambac jasmine. Comes the heart with osmanthus, white flowers, balms. Dry down unveils patchouli, amber, benzoin, vanilla.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Flowerbomb Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: More concentrated, hence more glamorous and chic. Scent starts with bergamot, sambac jasmine. Comes the heart with osmanthus, white flowers, balms. Dry down unveils patchouli, amber, benzoin, vanilla.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Flowerbomb Midnight Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Flowerbomb Midnight by Viktor&Rolf is a Floral fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Flowerbomb Midnight was launched in 2019. Top notes are black currant and pomegranate; middle notes are night blooming jasmine and peony; base notes are vanilla and white musk.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Ruby Orchid Eau De Parfum 100ml
description: Flowerbomb Ruby Orchid by Viktor&Rolf is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. Flowerbomb Ruby Orchid was launched in 2021.  Top notes are Peach and Vine; middle note is Orchid; base note is Vanilla Bean.

product_name: Viktor & Rolf Ruby Orchid Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Flowerbomb Ruby Orchid by Viktor&Rolf is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. Flowerbomb Ruby Orchid was launched in 2021.  Top notes are Peach and Vine; middle note is Orchid; base note is Vanilla Bean.

Peach Liqueur is the most recent addition to the portfolio and delivers the juicy flavour of fresh, ripe peaches. Vok Peach Liqueur brings a fruity depth in some of the most delicious cocktails recipes. Alcohol:  17%

Crème de Menthe Liqueur is a clean and crisp tasting liqueur made by blending an assortment of mint essences. Its a versatile liqueur that can be enjoyed as an after dinner drink, a simple mixer or the key to a number of delicious cocktails. Alcohol:  17%

Blue Curacao Liqueur adds its distinctive vibrant blue colour to many classic cocktail recipes. This orange flavoured liqueur resembles the dried peel of oranges found on the Caribbean Island of Curacao. Alcohol:  17%
Triple Sec Liqueur is a very popular liqueur that delivers the fresh flavour of orange peel. It is one of the most versatile liqueurs being used as a mixer and as a cocktail ingredient. Alcohol:  17%

product_name: Tissot Bella Ora Round Black Leather Women's Watch
description: Presenting the Tissot T-Lady, a stylish Swiss-Made watch specifically designed for women. Powered by a quartz movement, this watch showcases a classic round 38mm stainless steel case coupled with a pristine white dial under a scratch-resistant sapphire crystal. A convenient date feature at 3 o'clock ensures you're always on schedule. The black leather strap enhances the sophisticated feel and fastens securely with a pin buckle. With a closed case back and 30m water resistance, the T-Lady merges timeless elegance with durability, creating an accessory that complements any ensemble. T103.210.16.018.00

product_name: Tissot PR 100 Sport Chic Stainless Steel Women's Watch
description: The Tissot PR 100 is a classic watch destined to be worn often and for every occasion. It features the simple and elegant face the collection is loved for, with the pared-back aesthetic symbolizing luxury, quality and classic style. This women's model from the Tissot PR 100 collection has a 316L stainless steel case and a silver-colored dial. T101.910.11.036.00

product_name: Tiffany & Co. Tiffany & Love For Him Eau De Toilette 50ml
description: Tiffany & Love Eau de Toilette for Him is a citrusy, aromatic fragrance with a fresh and masculine scent. An enticing composition, the scent begins with oils of ginger, mandarin and cardamom. At the heart is a juniper-cypress blend, a co-distillation process created exclusively for Tiffany, which brings a sense of modernity to the fragrance. Sandalwood, vetiver and the common ingredient of the duo, the signature blue sequoia note, complete the base of this masterful composition.

product_name: Thierry Mugler Aura Eau De Toilette Spray 90ml
description: Aura MUGLER Eau de Toilette is a fragrance that fuses fruity freshness and feline sensuality. A unique creation with instinctive notes and a fruity freshness, Eau de Toilette.

product_name: Thierry Mugler Aura Eau De Parfum 30ml
description: Listen to your instinct. aura mugler, the latest mugler fragrance, invites you to reconnect with your inner nature and to unleash all your femininity and your aura. by blending botanical freshness with feline sensuality, the fragrance releases vibrant notes with an assertive personality. the aura mugler eau de parfum comes to life in an iconic bottle shaped like a universal symbol – the heart, the very source of life and the realm of the emotions. this mugler creation is adorned with the brand’s metallic m. the spray bottle may be refilled with refill bottles.

product_name: The Singleton Radiant Spring Garden Single Malt Scotch Whisky 1L
description: Inspired by springtime gardens with blossoming fruit trees. This whisky has been matured in our Select White Oak casks. The result is an exceptional expression of Glendullan’s quintessential bright and fruity character.  Alcohol:  40%

product_name: The Singleton Golden Autumn Orchard Single Malt Scotch Whisky 1L
description: Inspired by autumnal orchards with fruity aromas and honied scents. To evoke the season richness, the whisky has been Double Oak Matured in ex-Bourbon and American White Oak casks. The result is a delectable Single Malt, ripe with sweet indulgence. Alcohol:  41.8%

Whispering Angel is today’s worldwide reference for Provence rosé. Made from Grenache, Cinsault and Rolle (Vermentino), its pale color is pleasing to the eye and draws one in. The rewarding taste profile is full and lush while being bone dry with a smooth finish. Whispering Angel's fine and elegant aromatic strcuture provides additional length wihtout losing crispness. Tasting Notes: Aroma: Great purity with subtle notes of citrus fruits and fresh red fruits. Palate: Round and oily on the palate supported by a nice acidity giving  relief. Finish: Fine and elegant aromatic structure providing additional length without losing crispness. Alcohol:  13%

Dow's old Tawnies are well known for their remarkable raisiny, dried fruit flavours, exquisite creamy texture and an exceptionally long, lingering finish. Dow's Twenty Years Old Tawny is the perfectly balanced tawny. The delicate flavours acquired through long ageing combine perfectly with the rich and subtle mature fruit. Light amber and tawny colour, showing mature raisiny fruit aromas with hints of honey and caramel. Dow's Twenty Years Old Tawny has a rich and nutty palate, with wonderful balance. A clean crisp finish and a soft lingering aftertaste make this an unforgettable Port on any occasion. Alcohol:  20%
Disaronno is a traditional almond liqueur with a delicate and smooth taste, produced using a recipe passed through generations since 1525. Alcohol:  28%

product_name: 23Rd Street Distillery Signature & Tropical Gin Twin Pack
description: SIGNATURE GIN:  You’re trying to be nonchalant with your sophisticated botanical gin but all the while tiny explosions of Riverland sunshine tickle your palate. It’s the underlying citrus from fresh local mandarin and lime that makes Twenty Third Street gin a particularly jovial drop.  TROPICAL GIN:  Bright, juicy tropical fruit flavours burst forth over a background hum of sophisticated botanicals. Flavours of radiant Australian summer sun, and refreshing leafy shade. Real mango, pineapple, passionfruit and finger lime in every bottle evoke decadent holiday vibes. Splash some sunshine around. Alcohol:  40%

Sweet with light peat to start off with. Bourbon cask influence as I pick up vanilla, some smoked honey (if it’s not a thing, it should be a thing), pear drops and light toffee. Cereal developing latterly. Taste: Light on the peat and there’s a youthful note there but it’s not harsh. The whole thing has a softness about it. The honey’s there but it’s joined by citrus and pudding spices. Very approachable. Alcohol:  40%

Clear color. Aromas and flavors of anise candy coating, frosted fruit cake, honey butter, and pine sap with a silky, bright, dry-yet-fruity medium-to-full body and a smooth, engaging, medium-length finish revealing accents of lemon and papaya custard, pink peppercorn, and lady grey tea. A polished, mellow, earthy gin that will excel in creamy gin cocktails. Alcohol:  37.5%

Tenjaku is a Japanese character for both the skylark (Hibari), the beloved herald of spring, and this masterful malt whisky. It has an agreeably pure, mellow flavor, similar to the clear exquisite song of a small bird. The color of this fantastic whisky is pale gold. Aromas of fresh grain, banana bread with raisins, toasted walnuts, and honey-drizzled pears, with a supple, crisp, dryish light-to-medium body and a smooth, interesting medium-long finish of melon, smoked peppercorns, pimiento, marinated mushrooms, and banana nougat.

An easy pouch full of delicious Twix bars in a mini format. Share them with all your friends or family - there's plenty to go round. Ingredients: Sugar, glucose syrup, wheat flour, palm fat, cocoa butter, skimmed milk powder, cocoa mass, lactose, milk fat, whey powder (from milk), fat reduced cocoa, emulsifier (soya lecithin), salt, raising agent (sodium hydrogen carbonate), natural vanilla extract. Allergens:  Contains gluten (wheat), milk, soya Warnings:  May contain traces of hazelnut, almond, gluten (barley, oats).

product_name: Versace Women's 2-Piece Dylan Turquoise Eau De Toilette Travel Set
description: Discover the Dylan Turquoise Travel Set, featuring a 100ml Eau de Toilette and 100ml Body Lotion. Inspired by the Mediterranean, this set evokes freshness and vitality with its vibrant notes of citrus and aromatic florals. Perfect for travel, it embodies a breezy, carefree spirit, leaving you refreshed and invigorated wherever you go. Fragrance Notes: Top: Mandarin essence, lemon primofiore essence, pink pepper Heart: Blackcurrant, buds absolute, jasmine petals, freesia, guava Base: Clearwood®, vibrant woods, musk Olfactory family: Floral, woody, musk

product_name: Tiffany & Co. Tiffany & Love For Her Eau De Parfum 50ml
description: Tiffany & Love Eau de Parfum for Her is a modern yet feminine floral woody scent. The fragrance opens with a burst of bright and sparkling top notes, beginning with blue basil–a botanical ingredient developed exclusively for Tiffany – paired with grapefruit for an aromatic crispness. The sweet floral bouquet of neroli is at the heart of the fragrance, with a woody blend of blue sequoia, vetiver and cedarwood at the base, creating a faceted and feminine scent.

product_name: Versace Crystal Noir Eau De Toilette 90ml
description: This precious fragrance, inspired by haute couture, centers around the sweet yet subtle gardenia flower. Fresh gardenia blends seamlessly with transparent amber, creating a seductive and luminous allure. Perfectly capturing the contradictions of every woman—sweet yet sensual, earthy yet sophisticated—this scent is an embodiment of elegance and allure. Fragrance Notes: Top: Cardamom, pepper, ginger Heart: Gardenia, peony, orange flower Base: Amber, sandalwood, musk Olfactory family: Floral, oriental

This masterfully blended whisky features a agreeably pure, mellow flavour. Made in the beautiful surroundings of Mt Fuji using carefully selected whiskies and the finest natural spring waters which are expertly blended to create this distinctive whisky.   Alcohol:  40%

product_name: The Glenlivet Groundbreaker Collection Single Malt Scotch Whisky 700ml
description: The Glenlivet Groundbreaker Collection is a limited-edition series celebrating travel and creatives who forge their own path. In this first Chapter One: The Journey Inwards, we’ve collaborated with renowned artist Red Hong Yi to reflect upon how unique travel experiences shape who we become. The first ever TGL whisky selectively finished in both heavily charred oak and red wine casks. This unique finish on The Glenlivet’s signature style delivers one of the most approachable expressions in our portfolio. Alcohol:  40%

Ready for flavour? At The Jelly Bean Factory we're obsessed with flavour. You too? Good. Join us in our flavour adventure. The Pop-a-bean one bean pops out per time! We've got 36 HUGE flavours waiting for you. We bet you can't just eat one. The Jelly Bean Factory. YES. That's flavour.

product_name: The Jelly Bean Factory 36 Flavour Gourmet Mix Atrium Box 225g
description: The Jelly Bean Factory are the best sharing snack – but only if there’s enough to share. This packaging contains 36 huge flavors, can you guess which flavor? The gourmet beans from The Jelly Bean Factory are made with 100% natural flavors and no artificial colors. The Jelly Bean Factory assortment is gluten free, and gelatine free.

product_name: The Jelly Bean Factory 18 Fruit Cocktails Mix Tube 175g
description: The Jelly Bean Factory are the best sharing snack – but only if there’s enough to share. This tube contains 18 Fruity flavors, can you guess which flavor? The gourmet beans from The Jelly Bean Factory are made with 100% natural flavors and no artificial colors. The Jelly Bean Factory assortment is gluten free, and gelatine free.

The only bourbon-based liqueur on the market, Wild Turkey liqueur brings out the best flavours of premium bourbon, but with real honey to give it a sweetness that's hard to resist. The palate is a bit like syrup and glides around the mouth with obvious notes of vanilla and citrus. Perfectly suited for after-dinner consumption, it rounds-out Wild Turkey's portfolio of exceptional products. Wild Turkey Liqueur also marries well with Wild Turkey Bourbon to make a Kentucky-style Golden Nail. It also goes well with vanilla ice cream, pecan pie, or as an ingredient in a butterscotch sauce. Alcohol:  35.5%
Produced with a corn dominate mash, wild turkey's 86.8 proof has a deep golden colour and exceptional taste a fine example of bourbon flavour at an affordable price. 43.3% Alc./Vol.

product_name: The Antipodes Gin Co Organic Pink Gin 700ml
description: Australia’s first certified organic pink gin is a fragrant and floral garden of chamomile flowers, tart Kakadu plum, refreshing citrus and notes of strawberry pink musk sticks. Alcohol:  40%

Smooth and richly colored, Wild Turkey Straight Kentucky Bourbon Whiskey is a genuine super-premium bourbon carefully crafted in the heart of Kentucky. Wild Turkey 8 Year-Old offers a lesson in traditional American values, most notably, the refusal to compromise on standards of excellence. Wild Turkey 8 Year-Old has an exceptionally soft, but rich aroma for a high proof bourbon, due to quality at all stages of making and aging for 8 years. Its taste is powerful and rich with caramel, vanilla and notes of honey and brown sugar. The finish is very long, rich and full-bodied, powerful, yet soothing.  Alcohol:  50.5%

An 81 Proof bourbon crafted by Wild Turkey associate distiller Eddie Russell son of master distiller Jimmy. Palate: Rich and thick, notes of caramel, manuka honey and fudge, hints of rhubarb and custard sweets and oily espresso beans. Finish: Caramel and coffee, hints of Black Forest honey and Hot Cross Buns. Charred and spicy.  Alcohol: 40.5%.

product_name: The Jelly Bean Factory 9 Sours Mix Tube 175g
description: The Jelly Bean Factory are the best sharing snack – but only if there’s enough to share. This tube contains 9 Sour flavors, can you guess which flavor? The gourmet beans from The Jelly Bean Factory are made with 100% natural flavors and no artificial colors. The Jelly Bean Factory assortment is gluten free, and gelatine free.

product_name: The Antipodes Gin Co Organic Gin 700ml
description: Antipodes Original Organic Gin - Australia’s first certified organic, carbon neutral gin. A fresh partnership of orange and lemon peel, native lemon myrtle dryness and layering, warmth of pepperberry, lingering notes of complementary herbs and spices. Alcohol:  45%

Niigata is known in Japan for its Three White treasures, i.e. snow, rice and sake, and a naturally blessed environment for pure water source. Made in Niigata, SHINOBU (meaning Forbearance in Japanese) Whisky is hand crafted by the creative master blender, Mr. Usami. He carefully selects whisky from around the world and first matures this in ex-Sherry and ex-Bourbon casks. Then finished in precious Japanese Mizunara oak and further matured in Japan. The result is a unique fusion of flavours and dynamic explosion across the palate. Displaying characters of plums, mint, baking spices, vanilla, citrus, toasty oak. Smooth and easy to drink. All natural with no colouring. Alcohol:  43%

Indulge in the luxurious flavours of Japan with our Premium Japanese Whisky Tasting Experience. This experience offers a journey through the rich and diverse world of Japanese whisky, allowing you to sample some of the finest and most sought-after blends from the Shinobu Distillery. This premium Japanese whisky tasting experience is a must for anyone who appreciates the art of fine spirits. Whether you’re a seasoned whisky enthusiast or a curious novice, this is an opportunity to taste some of the most exceptional whiskies in the world. This set contains:  4 x The Shinobu Whisky 50ml Alcohol:  43%

For this, “The Botanist”, small-batch, artisanal Islay gin we use nine of the classic gin aromatics – orris root, cassia bark, coriander seed, etc – and augment these with a heady harvest of 22 local botanicals, hand-picked by our expert foraging team from the windswept hills, peat bogs and Atlantic shores of this Hebridean island of Islay. Alcohol:  46%

product_name: The Glenlivet Single Malt Whisky Scotland Founder'S Reserve 1L Bottle 40%
description:
The exceptional character of The Glenlivet spirit is apparent even before the cask ageing process begins, a result of the unique lantern shaped pot stills we use at The Glenlivet. For The Glenlivet Founder's Reserve, skilful selection of casks enhances the signature fruity flavours of The Glenlivet with traditional oak casks being complemented by selective use of American first-fill casks to give a hint of creamy sweetness – creating an exceptionally well-balanced and smooth malt.
 Nose: Delicate aromas of citrus fruit, notably sweet orange Taste: Sweet, fruit notes of zesty oranges and pears, with a hint of candy, toffee apples

The Botanist is a gin of layered complexity. A progressive exploration of the botanical heritage of the isle of Islay. Nine classic gin botanicals are augmented by 22 local herbs and flowers, foraged responsibly and by hand from the hills, shores and bogs of this fertile Hebridean island. This fascinating seasonal cocktail is then slow "simmer" distilled in a unique Lomond pot-still. Affectionately known as "Ugly Betty" by the master distiller Jim McEwan, the still prefers to work at low-pressure and won't be rushed. So the precious botanicals are gently coaxed into releasing their complex, signature aromatics. The result is quicksilver: a highly distinctive, complex, floral gin with impeccable provenance; a truly artisanal, hand-crafted labour of love.
Great depth of ripe plum and blackberry fruit flavours. Full-bodied wine with a succulent palate, lively spices and fine velvety tannins. Alcohol:  14.5%
A faithful expression of the site – beautiful, haunting aromatics, fine sandy tannins and wonderful, memorable length on the palate.  Alcohol:  14.5%

Not your average Shiraz! On the nose there are peaches, ripe nectarine, wild raspberry and a little spice. The palate is soft and slurpy, the texture silky and any tannins just add a little seasoning – like macerated strawberries and black pepper. Turning a previously undervalued resource into something that is hugely enjoyable and ultimately gorgeous. Alcohol:  14.5%

The Great Escape is our benchmark, cooler climate Chardonnay produced from fruit grown in elevated vineyard sites which allow for a long ripening period which helps to maintain the natural sugar and acid balance of the grape. With moderate alcohol, focussed, crisp citrus fruit and a mouth-watering finish, this is an accomplished, truly modern style of this noble variety. Alcohol:  12.5%

product_name: The Antipodes Gin Co Organic Chai Gin 700ml
description: Australia’s first certified organic spice inspired chai gin. A full and refreshing masala blend of Ceylon tea, sweet cinnamon, chamomile, fennel and pepperberry whilst chocolate and vanilla cradle punchy citrus and fruit notes from cardamom and coriander. A spice trade trove of 13 exotic and native botanicals awaits a transformative splash of ginger beer – the mouth party starts. Alcohol:  40%

Fruit for Thorny Devil comes from a variety of some of the finest vineyards in McLaren Vale. Old bush trained vines and sandy, mineral strewn vineyards ensure that this is amongst our most delicious Grenaches. Alcohol:  14%

product_name: The Shinobu Lightly Peat Gift Set 700ml
description: Tasting Notes: Nose: Smells creamy and minty with some light peat and a touch of lemon. Hints of charcoal smoke and ash Palate: The peat tastes stronger on the palate, mingled with notes of charcoal smoke, ash, and dry grass and a hint of saltiness Finish: Lingering taste of roasted wood with lots of sweetness from roasted malt Alcohol:  43%

Grenache is Australia’s signature grape variety and we’re slightly obsessed with it. Utilising a range of premium vineyards across South Australia, we’ve crafted a wine that captures all that is good about Grenache. Aromatic, deceptively light but with beautiful wild fruit, and slurpy, supple tannins. Alcohol:  14.5%

product_name: Tiffany & Co. Sheer Eau De Toilette 75ml
description: A bright and sparkling interpretation of the signature fragrance, Tiffany Sheer Eau de Toilette is a vibrant floral scent with notes of ylang ylang, black currant and the noble iris.

product_name: Tiffany & Co. Tiffany & Love For Her Eau De Parfum 90ml
description: Tiffany & Love Eau de Parfum for Her is a modern yet feminine floral woody scent. The fragrance opens with a burst of bright and sparkling top notes, beginning with blue basil–a botanical ingredient developed exclusively for Tiffany – paired with grapefruit for an aromatic crispness. The sweet floral bouquet of neroli is at the heart of the fragrance, with a woody blend of blue sequoia, vetiver and cedarwood at the base, creating a faceted and feminine scent.
Easy to carry and fun to share! Tic Tac® Bottle – shaped like a ultra-large Tic Tac® - contains 200 Mint flavored pills to satisfy even the long haul traveler.

Arnott's Tim Tam Chewy Caramel biscuits are made with a combination of crunchy biscuit, chewy caramel centre, wrapped in a smooth chocolate coating.

Dial designs include some of the watch industry’s most iconic features and the collection offers a choice of details including Clous de Paris, Roman numerals and indexes and even Top Wesselton diamonds or an open heart dial.
